# RFC 8017 PKCS #1: RSA Cryptographic Specification V2.2

## Abstract

- Implementation of the Public Key Cryptography using RSA Algorithm
- Cryptographic Primitives
- Encryption Schemes
- Signatures Schemes with Appendix
- ASN.1 syntax for representing keys
- ASN.1 syntax for identifying the schemes

## Obsoletes

- RFC 3447 PKCS #1: RSA Cryptographic Specification V2.1
